OL,3,CAppeal to raise #45,000 to restore
OL,4,C'Shot at Dawn' war memorial
OL,6,FThe National Memorial Arboretum in is
OL,7,Fattempting to raise #45,000 to restore
OL,8,Fone of its memorials.
OL,10,FThe 'Shot at Dawn' Memorial
OL,11,Fcommemorates 309 British and
OL,12,FCommonwealth soldiers who were shot
OL,13,Ffor desertion, cowardice, striking a
OL,14,Fsenior officer, disobeying a lawful
OL,15,Forder, casting away arms, mutiny and
OL,16,Fsleeping at post during the .
OL,18,FMost of the soldiers who were shot
OL,19,Fwere sentenced after a short trial and
OL,20,Fweren't given fair opportunity to
OL,21,Fdefence.
